r : function(ev){} //click 事件\n...</div><div class='long'><p>点击事件的处理函数，快速配置点击事件而不需要写listeners属性</p>\n\n<pre><code>   var list = new <a href=\"#!/api/BUI.List.SimpleList\" rel=\"BUI.List.SimpleList\" class=\"docClass\">BUI.List.SimpleList</a>({\n     handler : function(ev){} //click 事件\n   });\n   list.render();\n </code></pre>\n\n</div></div></div><div id='cfg-hasErrorProperty' class='member  inherited'><a href='#' class='side expandable'><span>&nbsp;</span></a><div class='title'><div class='meta'><a href='#!/api/BUI.Data.AbstractStore' rel='BUI.Data.AbstractStore' class='defined-in docClass'>BUI.Data.AbstractStore</a><br/><a href='source/abstractstore.html#BUI-Data-AbstractStore-cfg-hasErrorProperty' target='_blank' class='view-source'>view source</a></div><a href='#!/api/BUI.Data.AbstractStore-cfg-hasErrorProperty' class='name expandable'>hasErrorProperty</a> : <a href=\"#!/api/String\" rel=\"String\" class=\"docClass\">String</a><span class=\"signature\"></span></div><div class='description'><div class='short'>是否存在错误,加载数据时如果返回错误，此字段表示有错误发生\n\n  //可以修改接收的后台参数的含义\n  var store = new Store({\n    url : 'data.json',\n    errorProperty ...</div><div class='long'><p>是否存在错误,加载数据时如果返回错误，此字段表示有错误发生</p>\n\n<pre><code>  //可以修改接收的后台参数的含义\n  var store = new Store({\n    url : 'data.json',\n    errorProperty : 'errorMsg', //存放错误信息的字段(error)\n    hasErrorProperty : 'isError', //是否错误的字段（hasError)\n    root : 'data',               //存放数据的字段名(rows)\n    totalProperty : 'total'     //存放记录总数的字段名(results)\n  });\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>Defaults to: <code>&#39;hasError&#39;</code></p></div></div></div><div id='cfg-listeners' class='member  inherited'><a href='#' class='side expandable'><span>&nbsp;</span></a><div class='title'><div class='meta'><a href='#!/api/BUI.Observable' rel='BUI.Observable' class='defined-in docClass'>BUI.Observable</a><br/><a href='source/observable.html#BUI-Observable-cfg-listeners' target='_blank' class='view-source'>view source</a></div><a href='#!/api/BUI.Observable-cfg-listeners' class='name expandable'>listeners</a> : <a href=\"#!/api/Object\" rel=\"Object\" class=\"docClass\">Object</a><span class=\"signature\"></span></div><div class='description'><div class='short'>初始化事件,快速注册事件\n\n   var list = new BUI.List.SimpleList({\n     listeners : {\n       itemclick : function(ev){},\n       it...</div><div class='long'><p>初始化事件,快速注册事件</p>\n\n<pre><code>   var list = new <a href=\"#!/api/BUI.List.SimpleList\" rel=\"BUI.List.SimpleList\" class=\"docClass\">BUI.List.SimpleList</a>({\n     listeners : {\n       itemclick : function(ev){},\n       itemrendered : function(ev){}\n     },\n     items : []\n   });\n   list.render();\n </code></pre>\n\n</div></div></div><div id='cfg-pageSize' class='member  not-inherited'><a href='#' class='side expandable'><span>&nbsp;</span></a><div class='title'><div class='meta'><span class='defined-in' rel='BUI.Data.Store'>BUI.Data.Store</span><br/><a href='source/store.html#BUI-Data-Store-cfg-pageSize' target='_blank' class='view-source'>view source</a></div><a href='#!/api/BUI.Data.Store-cfg-pageSize' class='name expandable'>pageSize</a> : <a href=\"#!/api/Number\" rel=\"Number\" class=\"docClass\">Number</a><span class=\"signature\"></span></div><div class='description'><div class='short'>每页多少条记录,默认为null,此时不分页，当指定了此值时分页\n\n //当请求的数据分页时\n var store = new Store({\n   url : 'data.json',\n   pageSize : 30\n }); ...</div><div class='long'><p>每页多少条记录,默认为null,此时不分页，当指定了此值时分页</p>\n\n<pre><code> //当请求的数据分页时\n var store = new Store({\n   url : 'data.json',\n   pageSize : 30\n });\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>Defaults to: <code>{}</code></p></div></div></div><div id='cfg-params' class='member  inherited'><a href='#' class='side expandable'><span>&nbsp;</span></a><div class='title'><div class='meta'><a href='#!/api/BUI.Data.AbstractStore' rel='BUI.Data.AbstractStore' class='defined-in docClass'>BUI.Data.AbstractStore</a><br/><a href='source/abstractstore.html#BUI-Data-AbstractStore-cfg-params' target='_blank' class='view-source'>view source</a></div><a href='#!/api/BUI.Data.AbstractStore-cfg-params' class='name expandable'>params</a> : <a href=\"#!/api/Object\" rel=\"Object\" class=\"docClass\">Object</a><span class=\"signature\"></span></div><div class='description'><div class='short'>初始化时查询的参数，在初始化时有效\n\nvar store = new Data.Store({\n    url : 'data.php',  //设置加载数据的URL\n    autoLoad : true,    //创建Store...</div><div class='long'><p>初始化时查询的参数，在初始化时有效</p>\n\n<pre><code>var store = new Data.Store({\n    url : 'data.php',  //设置加载数据的URL\n    autoLoad : true,    //创建Store时自动加载数据\n    params : {         //设置请求时的参数\n      id : '1',\n      type : '1'\n    }\n  });\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>Defaults to: <code>{}</code></p></div></div></div><div id='cfg-proxy' class='member  inherited'><a href='#' class='side expandable'><span>&nbsp;</span></a><div class='title'><div class='meta'><a href='#!/api/BUI.Data.AbstractStore' rel='BUI.Data.AbstractStore' class='defined-in docClass'>BUI.Data.AbstractStore</a><br/><a href='source/abstractstore.html#BUI-Data-AbstractStore-cfg-proxy' target='_blank' class='view-source'>view source</a></div><a href='#!/api/BUI.Data.AbstractStore-cfg-proxy' class='name expandable'>proxy</a> : <a href=\"#!/api/Object\" rel=\"Object\" class=\"docClass\">Object</a>|<a href=\"#!/api/BUI.Data.Proxy\" rel=\"BUI.Data.Proxy\" class=\"docClass\">BUI.Data.Proxy</a><span class=\"signature\"></span></div><div class='description'><div class='short'>数据代理对象,用于加载数据的ajax配置，BUI.Data.Proxy\n\n  var store = new Data.Store({\n    url : 'data.php',  //设置加载数据的URL\n    autoLoad ...</div><div class='long'><p>数据代理对象,用于加载数据的ajax配置，<a href=\"#!/api/BUI.Data.Proxy\" rel=\"BUI.Data.Proxy\" class=\"docClass\">BUI.Data.Proxy</a></p>\n\n<pre><code>  var store = new Data.Store({\n    url : 'data.php',  //设置加载数据的URL\n    autoLoad : true,    //创建Store时自动加载数据\n    proxy : {\n      method : 'post',\n      dataType : 'jsonp'\n    }\n  });\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>Defaults to: <code>{shared: false, value: {}}</code></p></div></div></div><div id='cfg-remoteSort' class='member  not-inherited'><a href='#' class='side expandable'><span>&nbsp;</span></a><div class='title'><div class='meta'><span class='defined-in' rel='BUI.Data.Store'>BUI.Data.Store</span><br/><a href='source/store.html#BUI-Data-Store-cfg-remoteSort' target='_blank' class='view-source'>view source</a></div><a href='#!/api/BUI.Data.Store-cfg-remoteSort' class='name expandable'>remoteSort</a> : <a href=\"#!/api/Boolean\" rel=\"Boolean\" class=\"docClass\">Boolean</a><span class=\"signature\"></span></div><div class='description'><div class='short'>是否远程排序，默认状态下内存排序\n  - 由于当前Store存储的不一定是数据源的全集，所以此配置项需要重新读取数据\n  - 在分页状态下，进行远程排序，会进行全集数据的排序，并返回首页的数据\n  - remoteSort为 fals...</div><div class='long'><p>是否远程排序，默认状态下内存排序\n  - 由于当前Store存储的不一定是数据源的全集，所以此配置项需要重新读取数据\n  - 在分页状态下，进行远程排序，会进行全集数据的排序，并返回首页的数据\n  - remoteSort为 false的情况下，仅对当前页的数据进行排序</p>\n<p>Defaults to: <code>false</code></p></div></div></div><div id='cfg-root' class='member  not-inherited'><a href='#' class='side expandable'><span>&nbsp;</span></a><div class='title'><div class='meta'><span class='defined-in' rel='BUI.Data.Store'>BUI.Data.Store</span><br/><a href='source/store.html#BUI-Data-Store-cfg-root' target='_blank' class='view-source'>view source</a></div><a href='#!/api/BUI.Data.Store-cfg-root' class='name expandable'>root</a> : <a href=\"#!/api/String\" rel=\"String\" class=\"docClass\">String</a><span class=\"signature\"></span></div><div class='description'><div class='short'>加载数据时，返回数据的根目录\n\n   //默认返回数据类型：\n   '{\"rows\":[{\"name\":\"abc\"},{\"name\":\"bcd\"}],\"results\":100}'\n  //可以修改接收的后台参数的含义\n  var s...</div><div class='long'><p>加载数据时，返回数据的根目录</p>\n\n<pre><code>   //默认返回数据类型：\n   '{\"rows\":[{\"name\":\"abc\"},{\"name\":\"bcd\"}],\"results\":100}'\n  //可以修改接收的后台参数的含义\n  var store = new Store({\n    url : 'data.json',\n    errorProperty : 'errorMsg', //存放错误信息的字段(error)\n    hasErrorProperty : 'isError', //是否错误的字段（hasError)\n    root : 'data',               //存放数据的字段名(rows)\n    totalProperty : 'total'     //存放记录总数的字段名(results)\n  });\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>Defaults to: <code>&#39;rows&#39;</code></p></div></div></div><div id='cfg-sortDirection' class='member  inherited'><a href='#' class='side expandable'><span>&nbsp;</span></a><div class='title'><div class='meta'><a href='#!/api/BUI.Data.Sortable' rel='BUI.Data.Sortable' class='defined-in docClass'>BUI.Data.Sortable</a><br/><a href='source/sortable.html#BUI-Data-Sortable-cfg-sortDirection' target='_blank' class='view-source'>view source</a></div><a href='#!/api/BUI.Data.Sortable-cfg-sortDirection' class='name expandable'>sortDirection</a> : <a href=\"#!/api/String\" rel=\"String\" class=\"docClass\">String</a><span class=\"signature\"></span></div><div class='description'><div class='short'>排序方向,'ASC'、'DESC' ...</div><div class='long'><p>排序方向,'ASC'、'DESC'</p>\n<p>Defaults to: <code>&#39;ASC&#39;</code></p></div></div></div><div id='cfg-sortField' class='member  inherited'><a href='#' class='side expandable'><span>&nbsp;</span></a><div class='title'><div class='meta'><a href='#!/api/BUI.Data.Sortable' rel='BUI.Data.Sortable' class='defined-in docClass'>BUI.Data.Sortable</a><br/><a href='source/sortable.html#BUI-Data-Sortable-cfg-sortField' target='_blank' class='view-source'>view source</a></div><a href='#!/api/BUI.Data.Sortable-cfg-sortField' class='name expandable'>sortField</a> : <a href=\"#!/api/String\" rel=\"String\" class=\"docClass\">String</a><span class=\"signature\"></span></div><div class='description'><div class='short'><p>排序字段</p>\n</div><div class='long'><p>排序字段</p>\n</div></div></div><div id='cfg-sortInfo' class='member  inherited'><a href='#' class='side expandable'><span>&nbsp;</span></a><div class='title'><div class='meta'><a href='#!/api/BUI.Data.Sortable' rel='BUI.Data.Sortable' class='defined-in docClass'>BUI.Data.Sortable</a><br/><a href='source/sortable.html#BUI-Data-Sortable-cfg-sortInfo' target='_blank' class='view-source'>view source</a></div><a href='#!/api/BUI.Data.Sortable-cfg-sortInfo' class='name expandable'>sortInfo</a> : <a href=\"#!/api/Object\" rel=\"Object\" class=\"docClass\">Object</a><span class=\"signature\"></span></div><div class='description'><div class='short'><p>排序信息</p>\n\n<ol>\n<li>field: 排序字段</li>\n<li>direction: 排序方向,ASC(默认),DESC</li>\n</ol>\n\n</div><div class='long'><p>排序信息</p>\n\n<ol>\n<li>field: 排序字段</li>\n<li>direction: 排序方向,ASC(默认),DESC</li>\n</ol>\n\n</div></div></div><div id='cfg-totalProperty' class='member  not-inherited'><a href='#' class='side expandable'><span>&nbsp;</span></a><div class='title'><div class='meta'><span class='defined-in' rel='BUI.Data.Store'>BUI.Data.Store</span><br/><a href='source/store.html#BUI-Data-Store-cfg-totalProperty' target='_blank' class='view-source'>view source</a></div><a href='#!/api/BUI.Data.Store-cfg-totalProperty' class='name expandable'>totalProperty</a> : <a href=\"#!/api/String\" rel=\"String\" class=\"docClass\">String</a><span class=\"signature\"></span></div><div class='description'><div class='short'>加载数据时，返回记录的总数的字段，用于分页\n\n   //默认返回数据类型：\n   '{\"rows\":[{\"name\":\"abc\"},{\"name\":\"bcd\"}],\"results\":100}'\n  //可以修改接收的后台参数的含义\n...</div><div class='long'><p>加载数据时，返回记录的总数的字段，用于分页</p>\n\n<pre><code>   //默认返回数据类型：\n   '{\"rows\":[{\"name\":\"abc\"},{\"name\":\"bcd\"}],\"results\":100}'\n  //可以修改接收的后台参数的含义\n  var store = new Store({\n    url : 'data.json',\n    errorProperty : 'errorMsg', //存放错误信息的字段(error)\n    hasErrorProperty : 'isError', //是否错误的字段（hasError)\n    root : 'data',               //存放数据的字段名(rows)\n    totalProperty : 'total'     //存放记录总数的字段名(results)\n  });\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>Defaults to: <code>&#39;results&#39;</code></p></div></div></div><div id='cfg-url' class='member  inherited'><a href='#' class='side expandable'><span>&nbsp;</span></a><div class='title'><div class='meta'><a href='#!/api/BUI.Data.AbstractStore' rel='BUI.Data.AbstractStore' class='defined-in docClass'>BUI.Data.AbstractStore</a><br/><a href='source/abstractstore.html#BUI-Data-AbstractStore-cfg-url' target='_blank' class='view-source'>view source</a></div><a href='#!/api/BUI.Data.AbstractStore-cfg-url' class='name expandable'>url</a> : <a href=\"#!/api/String\" rel=\"String\" class=\"docClass\">String</a><span class=\"signature\"></span></div><div class='description'><div class='short'>请求数据的地址，通过ajax加载数据，\n此参数设置则加载远程数据\n 你可以设置在proxy外部 \n\n  var store = new Data.Store({\n    url : 'data.php',  //设置加载数据的URL\n...</div><div class='long'><p>请求数据的地址，通过ajax加载数据，\n此参数设置则加载远程数据\n<strong> 你可以设置在proxy外部 </strong></p>\n\n<pre><code>  var store = new Data.Store({\n    url : 'data.php',  //设置加载数据的URL\n    autoLoad : true,    //创建Store时自动加载数据\n    proxy : {\n      method : 'post',\n      dataType : 'jsonp'\n    }\n  });\n</code></pre>\n\n\n<p><strong> 你也可以设置在proxy上 </strong></p>\n\n<pre><code>  var store = new Data.Store({\n    autoLoad : true,    //创建Store时自动加载数据\n    proxy : {\n      url : 'data.php',  //设置加载数据的URL\n      method : 'post',\n      dataType : 'jsonp'\n    }\n  });\n</code></pre>\n\n\n<p>否则把 {BUI.Data.Store#cfg-data}作为本地缓存数据加载</p>\n</div></div></div></div></div><div class='members-section'><div class='definedBy'>Defined By</div><h3 class='members-title icon-property'>Properties</h3><div class='subsection'><div id='property-_eventMap' class='member first-child inherited'><a href='#' class='side expandable'><span>&nbsp;</span></a><div class='title'><div class='meta'><a href='#!/api/BUI.Observable' rel='BUI.Observable' class='defined-in docClass'>BUI.Observable</a><br/><a href='source/observable.html#BUI-Observable-property-_eventMap' target='_blank' class='view-source'>view source</a></div><a href='#!/api/BUI.Observable-property-_eventMap' class='name expandable'>_eventMap</a> : <a href=\"#!/api/Object\" rel=\"Object\" class=\"docClass\">Object</a><span class=\"signature\"><span class='private' >private</span></span></div><div class='description'><div class='short'>绑定的事件 ...</div><div class='long'><p>绑定的事件</p>\n<p>Defaults to: <code>{}</code></p></div></div></div><div id='property-_events' class='member  inherited'><a href='#' class='side expandable'><span>&nbsp;</span></a><div class='title'><div class='meta'><a href='#!/api/BUI.Observable' rel='BUI.Observable' class='defined-in docClass'>BUI.Observable</a><br/><a href='source/observable.html#BUI-Observable-property-_events' target='_blank' class='view-source'>view source</a></div><a href='#!/api/BUI.Observable-property-_events' class='name expandable'>_events</a> : <a href=\"#!/api/Array\" rel=\"Array\" class=\"docClass\">Array</a><span class=\"signature\"><span class='private' >private</span></span></div><div class='description'><div class='short'>支持的事件名列表 ...</div><div class='long'><p>支持的事件名列表</p>\n<p>Defaults to: <code>[]</code></p></div></div></div><div id='property-data' class='member  inherited'><a href='#' class='side expandable'><span>&nbsp;</span></a><div class='title'><div class='meta'><a href='#!/api/BUI.Data.AbstractStore' rel='BUI.Data.AbstractStore' class='defined-in docClass'>BUI.Data.AbstractStore</a><br/><a href='source/abstractstore.html#BUI-Data-AbstractStore-property-data' target='_blank' class='view-source'>view source</a></div><a href='#!/api/BUI.Data.AbstractStore-property-data' class='name expandable'>data</a> : <a href=\"#!/api/Array\" rel=\"Array\" class=\"docClass\">Array</a><span class=\"signature\"></span></div><div class='description'><div class='short'><p>本地数据源</p>\n</div><div class='long'><p>本地数据源</p>\n</div></div></div><div id='property-deletedRecords' class='member  not-inherited'><a href='#' class='side expandable'><span>&nbsp;</span></a><div class='title'><div class='meta'><span class='defined-in' rel='BUI.Data.Store'>BUI.Data.Store</span><br/><a href='source/store.html#BUI-Data-Store-property-deletedRecords' target='_blank' class='view-source'>view source</a></div><a href='#!/api/BUI.Data.Store-property-deletedRecords' class='name expandable'>deletedRecords</a> : <a href=\"#!/api/Array\" rel=\"Array\" class=\"docClass\">Array</a><span class=\"signature\"><span class='private' >private</span></span></div><div class='description'><div class='short'>删除掉的纪录\n@readOnly ...</div><div class='long'><p>删除掉的纪录\n@readOnly</p>\n<p>Defaults to: <code>{shared: false, value: []}</code></p></div></div></div><div id='property-isStore' class='member  inherited'><a href='#' class='side expandable'><span>&nbsp;</span></a><div class='title'><div class='meta'><a href='#!/api/BUI.Data.AbstractStore' rel='BUI.Data.AbstractStore' class='defined-in docClass'>BUI.Data.AbstractStore</a><br/><a href='source/abstractstore.html#BUI-Data-AbstractStore-property-isStore' target='_blank' class='view-source'>view source</a></div><a href='#!/api/BUI.Data.AbstractStore-property-isStore' class='name expandable'>isStore</a> : <a href=\"#!/api/Boolean\" rel=\"Boolean\" class=\"docClass\">Boolean</a><span class=\"signature\"></span></div><div class='description'><div class='short'>是否是数据缓冲对象，用于判断对象 ...</div><div class='long'><p>是否是数据缓冲对象，用于判断对象</p>\n<p>Defaults to: <code>true</code></p></div></div></div><div id='property-lastParams' class='member  inherited'><a href='#' class='side expandable'><span>&nbsp;</span></a><div class='title'><div class='meta'><a href='#!/api/BUI.Data.AbstractStore' rel='BUI.Data.AbstractStore' class='defined-in docClass'>BUI.Data.AbstractStore</a><br/><a href='source/abstractstore.html#BUI-Data-AbstractStore-property-lastParams' target='_blank' class='view-source'>view source</a></div><a href='#!/api/BUI.Data.AbstractStore-property-lastParams' class='name expandable'>lastParams</a> : <a href=\"#!/api/Object\" rel=\"Object\" class=\"docClass\">Object</a><span class=\"signature\"></span></div><div class='description'><div class='short'>上次查询的参数\n@readOnly ...</div><div class='long'><p>上次查询的参数\n@readOnly</p>\n<p>Defaults to: <code>{shared: false, value: {}}</code></p></div></div></div><div id='property-matchFunction' class='member  not-inherited'>